  "body_html": "<p>The Men's Aurion 3L Ski Pant is designed for movement with a focus on breathability and strength. Made with the Toray Dermizax 20K / 20K membrane, these pants are highly breathable and stretchy with a wide cut.</p>\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Toray Dermizax 20K / 20K membrane construction</li>\n  <li>Wide cut design for enhanced movement</li>\n  <li>Long vents for temperature regulation</li>\n  <li>Adjustable belt for customized fit</li>\n  <li>Cordura\u00ae ankle reinforcement for durability</li>\n  <li>Integrated extra water-resistant snow gaiter</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Specifications</h3>\n<table>\n  <tr><td>Waist</td><td>29.9 - 32.3\"</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Hips</td><td>35.8 - 38.2\"</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Thigh</td><td>20.5 - 21.3\"</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Waist Bottom Height</td><td>42.5\"</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Inside Leg Height</td><td>31.9\"</td></tr>\n</table>",
